2019-12-20 06:36:02	clyybber	And inside it you can have result be some unowned ref. The ref is not allowed to be referenced by variables from outer scopes though, and this way they can guarantee that it is convertible to owned ref/iso
2019-12-20 06:36:07	clyybber	Araq: No at compile time
2019-12-20 06:36:20	clyybber	Its a smart idea.
