2019-12-20 06:37:50	clyybber	This explains it a bit better than I can
2019-12-20 06:38:28	clyybber	This means that when the recover expression finishes, any aliases to the result of the expression other than iso, val and tag ones won’t exist anymore. That makes it safe to “lift” the reference capability of the result of the expression.
